      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "## Window-over-window profile comparison\n\nBoth panels use the same host/container and profiling-dimension selector. Leave **container hostname** at `All` for host profiles, or select a container for container profiles. The **current window** is shown on the left; the right panel applies Grafana's native `timeShift: 1h` and therefore shows the preceding one-hour-shifted window. Each flame graph panel keeps Grafana's built-in **Top table** available.\n\nThe apiserver also implements the Pyroscope-compatible `querier.v1.QuerierService/Diff` RPC for clients that submit explicit baseline and comparison selections. This dashboard deliberately provides a directly verifiable side-by-side comparison with supported `queryType: profile` queries; it does not claim that Grafana Profiles Drilldown service discovery is configured.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.0.3",
      "title": "How to compare",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "grafana-pyroscope-datasource",
        "uid": "huatuo-apiserver-pyroscope"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 20,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "showFlameGraphOnly": false
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.0.3",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "grafana-pyroscope-datasource",
            "uid": "huatuo-apiserver-pyroscope"
          },
          "groupBy": [],
          "labelSelector": "{hostname=\"$hostname\",container_hostname=~\"${container_hostname:regex}\",profiling_scope=~\"${profiling_scope:regex}\",cpu=~\"${cpu:regex}\",pid=~\"${pid:regex}\",tgid=~\"${tgid:regex}\",cgroup_id=~\"${cgroup_id:regex}\",cgroup_path=~\"${cgroup_path:regex}\",process_group_id=~\"${process_group_id:regex}\",container_id=~\"${container_id:regex}\",lock_type=~\"${lock_type:regex}\"}",
          "maxNodes": 16384,
          "profileTypeId": "$type",
          "queryType": "profile",
          "refId": "A",
          "spanSelector": []
        }
      ],
      "title": "Current window — flame graph and Top table",
      "type": "flamegraph"
    },
    {
